{"html":"<br/>\n<h2>Fact Symbols with Injective Instances</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\">None</p><br/>\n<h2>Multiset Rewriting Rules</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) isend:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KU( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> K( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) irecv:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KD( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ONE:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Fr( ~sk ), Fr( ~random ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( revealSign(~random, ~sk) ), Key( ~sk ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) TWO:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( sig ), Key( ~sk ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Equality( revealVerify(sig, getMessage(sig), pk(~sk)), true ), A( )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) TWO:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( sig ), Key( ~sk ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Equality( z, true ), A( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_keyword\">variants</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC)<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1. ~sk   = ~sk.4<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sig   = sig.4<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;z     = revealVerify(sig.4, getMessage(sig.4), pk(~sk.4))<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2. ~sk   = ~x.4<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sig   = revealSign(x.5, ~x.4)<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;z     = true<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3. ~sk   = ~sk.6<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sig   = revealSign(x.4, x.5)<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;z     = revealVerify(revealSign(x.4, x.5), x.4, pk(~sk.6))<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span></p><br/>\n<h2>Restrictions of the Set of Traces</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">restriction</span> equality:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>x y #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Equality( x, y ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>x <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> y<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// safety formula</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;expanded formula:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>x y #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Equality( x, y ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>x <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> y<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span></p><br/>\n","title":"Multiset rewriting rules and restrictions"}